      "originalText": "TE source : RE only\nsteps: RE + intersection wwith TE +\n    create\noptional : user can choose to gen comment\n    and edit\nadaptive card had many flaky, rendering issue\nI fugured out the multiline comment fix day\nbefore demo\nsidecar is implemented by IC, extended by \n    each owning team\n\n",
